bug.short_desc: Html2TextReader.entity2Text(String) mangles all but 7 escape codes

long_desc.thetext:
org.eclipse.mylyn.internal.commons.core.Html2TextReader.entity2Text(String)
the last line of the method is:
return "&" + symbol; // not found //$NON-NLS-1$
it should be
return "&" + symbol + ";"; // not found //$NON-NLS-1$

Submitted related bug against jface:
391072: HTML2TextReader.entity2Text(String) mangles all but 7 escape codes https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=391072
Jacek, it looks like you know how to fix this problem. Can you submit a review to Gerrit including a test case?

Jacek, Steffen,
I have commit this but add //$NON-NLS-2$ at the end of the line. This was the same like in bug#391072 (http://git.eclipse.org/c/platform/eclipse.platform.text.git/commit/?id=7edcbfb6389bbbdbc14c57d31e0be01640833275).
Thanks for looking into this! Frank, can you submit a simple test case for this fix? We also need to cherry-pick it onto the 3.8.x branch.
